HEADWORD: Inodorous
<hw>In*o"dor*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>inodorus</ets>. See <er>In-</er> not, and <er>Odorous</er>.]</ety>
<def>Emitting no odor; without smell; scentless; odorless.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>In*o"dor*ous*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inoffensive</ent>⟦br⟧
